room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: Took a group of 8 adults, had a blast. We will definitely go again.

room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: We went here with some friends and ended up in a group of seven people. We tried the Area 51 room. We finished in 53 minutes and didn't need to use our extra five minutes. Time definitely flies and it was a lot of fun. We will definitely be doing it again and probably taking our kids.

room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: What a great place. Awesome time. We did the Area 51 room and can't wait to try the rest.
